  "title": "SUPERVISOR",
  "description": "<p>Supervisor Responsibilities:</p><p>•\tMaking sure employees that report to you meet performance expectations.</p><p>•\tGiving instructions or orders to subordinate employees.</p><p>•\tEnsuring that the work environment is safe, secure and healthy.</p><p>•\tMeeting deadlines.</p><p>•\tApproving work hours.</p><p>•\tEnsure great customer service at all levels.</p><p>Supervisor Requirements:</p><p>•\tPrevious leadership experience.</p><p>•\tExcellent communication skills.</p><p>•\tEye for detail and accuracy.</p><p>•\tReliable, with high integrity and strong work ethic.</p><p>•\tAbility to work as part of a team.</p><p>•\tProfessional appearance and attitude.</p><p>•\tComputer literacy.</p><p>•\tProactive organizational skills.</p><p>•\tHigh school diploma.</p><p>•\tAbility to keep a positive attitude in a fast-paced environment.</p><p></p><p></p><p></p>",
